Package org.gerstner.oauth2android

Most important classes that gets directly instantiated by the application.

See:
          Description

Class Summary
Client In OAuth 2.0 the client is the actual application requesting access to the protected resources of the resource owner.
OAuth The OAuth Object is the "control center" for all steps within the OAuth-flow.
ParameterList The ParameterList class extends the ArrayList for the sole purpose to make the handling of parameters easier.
Server The Server class contains all necessary information on the service providers urls and a few preferences regarding the behavior of the server.
